(Corrects loan size in first paragraph.)  Blue Water Iron Ore Terminal Ltd.,
an Indian unit of  Noble Group Ltd. (NOBL) , the Hong Kong-based
commodities trader, signed an $86 million project finance loan
that matures in 2023, according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  ICICI Bank Ltd. (ICICIBC) , Standard Chartered Plc and Sumitomo Mitsui
Banking Corp. helped arrange the facility, the data show.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katrina Nicholas in Singapore at 
